channel.title: Request Development Team
channel.description:
I am searching for an experienced coder to help me start my new RSPS. I am planning on making the server a 317 [PI] with stuff that will stand out. I am offering the coder both 40% donation profit and developer (CO) in game.
I will be purchasing a VPS and custom domain. I will be purchasing a TOP 10 advertise over time.
I am able to put the server on right away once I find my coder.
Contact me VIA skype if you are interested.
skype : rune.stem
